This was ecstatic experience.
Resistance to ecstatic experience and stringent conformity mutated into repressed energy, creating a “beat generation.” The antidote to this pathology was to release the madness.
Ecstatic experience manifests in many ways and can be accessed through numerous channels.
In The Art of Losing Control, Evans lays out several gateways to ecstatic experience—adjoining his own experimentation with current research.
One can appreciate the wonder of natural landscapes, the wildness of the earth, and still, miss out on ecstatic experience.